Third-party components
----------------------

This program is dynamically linked against the GNU Multiple Precision
Arithmetic Library (GMP).

  GMP - The GNU Multiple Precision Arithmetic Library
  Copyright (C) Free Software Foundation, Inc.
  Homepage: https://gmplib.org/
  Version linked against: 6.3.0

GMP is licensed under the GNU Lesser General Public License, version 3 or
later (LGPLv3+). The full text of the LGPLv3 is provided in
licenses/LGPL-3.0.txt, and the full text of the GPLv3 (which the LGPLv3
references) is provided in licenses/GPL-3.0.txt.

Source code for GMP
-------------------

The complete corresponding source code for GMP can be obtained from the
official GMP website:

    https://gmplib.org/download/gmp/

The exact version this binary was linked against (GMP 6.3.0) is available at:

    https://gmplib.org/download/gmp/gmp-6.3.0.tar.xz

This written offer is valid for at least three (3) years from the date of
distribution of this binary. To request the source on physical media, contact
the distributor of this program.

Relinking (LGPLv3 §4(d))
------------------------

The flagchecker binary is dynamically linked against libgmp.so.10. Users
may replace the system's GMP shared library with a modified version
compatible with the same ABI in order to produce a modified combined work,
in accordance with LGPLv3 §4(d)(1).

License compatibility
---------------------

The MPL-2.0 (covering flagchecker's own source) and LGPLv3 (covering GMP)
are compatible for distribution as a combined work in executable form.
See MPL-2.0 §3.3.
